- wp:paragraph -->\n<div class=\"col-xs-12 detail-desc\">\n<div class=\"content-fck\">\n<div class=\"content-fck-font-size\">\n<div class=\"box-des-detail this-one\">\n<p>Khi du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn TP Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c (An Giang) \u0111\u1ec3 tham quan, v\u00eda B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn tham quan v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m trong chuy\u1ebfn du Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"detail-content-body\" data-theme=\"0\">\n<p>Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 chu \u0111\u00e1o cho du kh\u00e1ch \u0111i l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam. D\u00f9 du kh\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0o ban ng\u00e0y hay bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i th\u00ec v\u1eabn chi\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3nh s\u1eafc thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed y\u00ean b\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1eafm m\u00ecnh trong kh\u00f4ng gian Ph\u1eadt Gi\u00e1o. Ng\u1ed3i tr\u00ean c\u00e1p treo, du kh\u00e1ch c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 bao qu\u00e1t to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 TP Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u2013 Campuchia. \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, khi tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1p treo v\u00e0o bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i, du kh\u00e1ch s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed se l\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 bi\u00ean th\u00f9y, v\u1edbi \u00e1nh \u0111\u00e8n lung linh \u1edf m\u1ecdi g\u00f3c nh\u00ecn.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_1-1708083921069.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 1.jpg -0\" width=\"1280\" height=\"822\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_1-1708083921069.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam lung linh s\u1eafc m\u00e0u.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<p>D\u1ecbp T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024, c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi khu du l\u1ecbch.<\/p>\n<p>Raper S\u00f3c N\u00e2u cho bi\u1ebft: Tuy\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cao t\u1ed1c t\u1eeb TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh xu\u1ed1ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1, r\u1ed3i di chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Mi\u1ebfu B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i, do r\u00fat ng\u1eafn th\u1eddi gian r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y. V\u00ec th\u1ebf, gia \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u00ean 30 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m du l\u1ecbch v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00eam, t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng ti\u1ebft Xu\u00e2n v\u00f9ng bi\u00ean gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u1ea9m th\u1ef1c v\u00f9ng mi\u1ec1n, tham gia c\u00e1c tr\u00f2 ch\u01a1i d\u00e2n gian c\u00f3 th\u01b0\u1edfng, nghe v\u1ecdng c\u1ed5, h\u00e1t v\u1ec1 l\u00f4 t\u00f4\u2026 \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m m\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ai \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam m\u1edbi c\u1ea3m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n<p>Ca s\u0129 Qu\u00e1ch Tu\u1ea5n Du chia s\u1ebb: \u201cVi\u1ebfng B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 n\u01a1i B\u00e0 ng\u1ef1, v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh t\u00e2m linh, v\u1eeba tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i, nhanh ch\u00f3ng, ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 c\u1ea3nh quan h\u00f9ng v\u0129, lung linh t\u1eeb tr\u00ean cao\u201d.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_2-1708083948960.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 2.jpg -0\" width=\"768\" height=\"484\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_2-1708083948960.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Khu Du l\u1ecbch Qu\u1ed1c gia N\u00fai Sam \u0111\u00f3n h\u00e0ng tr\u0103m ngh\u00ecn l\u01b0\u1ee3t du kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng, tham quan trong d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<p>C\u00f2n di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean Tuy\u1ec1n M\u1eadp cho bi\u1ebft, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y, khi \u0111\u1ea3nh l\u1ec5 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 xong ch\u1ec9 mong nhanh quay v\u1ec1 l\u1ea1i TP H\u1ed3 Ch\u00ed Minh, do m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian di chuy\u1ec3n, n\u1ebfu b\u1ecb k\u1eb9t xe th\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua t\u1eeb 16 -18 gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 m\u1edbi v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ebfn nay. V\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n b\u00e8 truy\u1ec1n tai cho bi\u1ebft chuy\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh h\u01b0\u01a1ng s\u1ebd tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n h\u01a1n, nhanh h\u01a1n khi \u0111i c\u00e1p treo l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh N\u00fai Sam, r\u1ed3i vi\u1ebfng b\u1ec7 B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9, chi\u00eam b\u00e1i t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ph\u1eadt Ng\u1ecdc song sinh v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn l\u1ed9c V\u00eda B\u00e0 &#8211; l\u00e0 t\u00fai c\u00e1t nh\u1ecf d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00e1t nhang, m\u00f3n qu\u00e0 n\u00e0y do Ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd Khu du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam t\u1eb7ng du kh\u00e1ch\u2026<\/p>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_3-1708083965019.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 3.jpg -0\" width=\"1259\" height=\"876\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_3-1708083965019.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_4-1708083983982.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 4.jpg -0\" width=\"1154\" height=\"741\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_4-1708083983982.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_5-1708083984435.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 5.jpg -1\" width=\"956\" height=\"592\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_5-1708083984435.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>C\u00e1c ngh\u1ec7 s\u0129, di\u1ec5n vi\u00ean, ca s\u0129 check-in t\u1ea1i Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_6-1708084080534.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 6.jpg -0\" width=\"1241\" height=\"839\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_6-1708084080534.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Du kh\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m t\u1ea1i Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_7-1708084104240.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 7.jpg -0\" width=\"1217\" height=\"792\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_7-1708084104240.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_8-1708084104740.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 8.jpg -1\" width=\"1030\" height=\"643\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_8-1708084104740.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Du kh\u00e1ch tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m c\u00e1p treo.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_10-1708084135538.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 10.jpg -0\" width=\"1280\" height=\"828\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_10-1708084135538.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_11-1708084135006.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 11.jpg -1\" width=\"1111\" height=\"687\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_11-1708084135006.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption><\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<figure class=\"image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_9-1708084134709.jpg\" alt=\"hinh 9.jpg -2\" width=\"1280\" height=\"804\" data-src=\"https:\/\/img.cand.com.vn\/resize\/800x800\/NewFiles\/Images\/2024\/02\/16\/Hinh_9-1708084134709.jpg\" data- title=\"\">\n<figcaption>Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3nh quan, d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 du kh\u00e1ch d\u1ecbp T\u1ebft Nguy\u00ean \u0111\u00e1n Gi\u00e1p Th\u00ecn 2024.<\/figcaption>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Khi du kh\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ebfn TP Ch\u00e2u \u0110\u1ed1c (An Giang) \u0111\u1ec3 tham quan, v\u00eda B\u00e0 Ch\u00faa X\u1ee9 N\u00fai Sam, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 Khu Du l\u1ecbch C\u00e1p treo N\u00fai Sam, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 thu h\u00fat h\u00e0ng ngh\u00ecn ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn tham quan v\u00e0 tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m trong chuy\u1ebfn du Xu\u00e2n v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":2408,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[79],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2403"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=2403"}],"version-history":[{"count":7,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2403\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":2503,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/2403\/revisions\/2503"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2408"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/captreonuisam.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=2403"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/c